 In the case of one woman's trash is another's treasure, Madisakwane has opened her heart to Pretoria businessman Nico Matlala who made headlines last year for notoriously kicking out his then fianc e KB from their Centurion home.So smitten is Madisakwane with the businessman, that she took to Instagram this week to share pictures of them on vacation in Durban last week."He says he loves my smile. Now I can't stop smiling. I even smile in my sleep," Madisakwane captioned one of the pictures with Matlala.